{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "16-15", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "曠野轟鳴", "storyInfo": "第四集團軍派來使者，希望女大公能在他們前去剿滅“叛亂”時保持沉默。博士等人為了向同伴傳遞消息，使用了研究所中的緊急通訊設備。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g2_farnorthgovernment", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodcracle", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說來奇怪……", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我很喜歡布列斯克的這個季節。", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有太陽的東升西落，沒有晝夜分明……人們也不用假裝一切都很明瞭。", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“多事之秋”，元帥也是這麼說的。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女大公殿下，時間緊迫。即使是在我享用您招待的這一杯熱茶的時間裡，局勢也在不斷變得緊張。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "元帥在等待您的答覆。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連葉甫根尼元帥都坐立難安了，看來烏薩斯真的面臨著巨大的麻煩。", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您完全正確。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這樣的局勢下，聖駿堡溫吞的反應將不被接受——這不只是元帥一人的意見。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "時至今日，他應該早已理解，他的父親在當年那場動亂中的舉措堪稱睿智——第四集團軍本會有比發配邊疆更壞的結局。", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼如今，年輕的葉甫根尼，是下定決心要衝往眼下亂局的第一線嗎？", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "永遠站在離危險最近的地方保護烏薩斯——元帥在履行烏薩斯軍人的天職。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的問題，在於您，女大公殿下。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "元帥需要您還願意維繫往日的合作。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是他對我的通知？", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個基於友誼的請求。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "元帥他非常重視與您的友誼，同樣也信任您的智慧。他相信，即使在這個時候，布列斯克與第四集團軍的利益也是緊密相連的。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何況他並不請求您做什麼額外的事——只要您的一個點頭。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來，他似乎認為這很容易。", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道他將我們的皇帝陛下當成一個蠢材嗎？難道維特議長也是一個蠢材嗎？", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#4$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是非此即彼的選擇……就像太陽不會與黑夜共存。", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#4$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "元帥非常理解您的處境，他當然願意為您分憂。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，一位“皇帝的利刃”的隕落，有非常充分的解釋空間，而元帥願意替您做出這個解釋。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“第四集團軍協助布列斯克剿滅了發生在遠北地區的叛亂”——只要您願意合作，集團軍呈交給聖駿堡的報告上，就只會有這樣一句話。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至不必點頭，您的沉默，元帥也可以接受。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……並非如此……如果元帥他真的理解我，就該知道我在意的從來不是來自聖駿堡的質疑……", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#4$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生活在我的領地內的人民，烏薩斯的人民……我在意的只有他們。", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#4$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "元帥理解您的仁慈，他向您保證，您劃下的線，沒有人可以逾越。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕的葉甫根尼，急躁的葉甫根尼……我又怎會願意看到我親愛的朋友以身涉險。", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#2$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕真的如他所願，我保持沉默，這也不過是在他前行的險路上抹去了一堆小小石頭，那些巨大的山石他又準備如何處置？", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#2$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些，就不勞女大公殿下煩憂了。無論是山石還是其他東西，元帥他有決心為烏薩斯戰勝所有敵人。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼……我是否可以理解為，已經得到了您的答覆？", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葉甫根尼元帥向您問好。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了烏薩斯的榮光。", "name": "嚴肅的烏薩斯軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1977_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切為了烏薩斯的榮光……", "name": "葉莉莎女大公"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1962_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g3_miningarea", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "1", "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "科謝尼婭，你還好嗎？不行的話我也可以抱著你們兩人一起跑！", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4208_wintim_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不用。我……還好……", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#8$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是不懂……我們為什麼……要這麼急著趕路？", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#8$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我有一個猜想……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line92"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "如果烏薩斯官方已經得知了礦脈的異變……;能讓遠北所有的礦區都陷入沉寂，只有一種解釋——", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line94", "option2": "line94"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "烏薩斯不會讓礦脈枯竭的消息傳播出去。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line96"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4208_wintim_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#3$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你看天空的顏色！", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們進來的時候，是這樣的嗎？", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#5$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4208_wintim_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不……這是我的幻覺嗎？", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#6$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4208_wintim_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼又是……這樣的顏色？", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#7$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g4_miningarea_polluted", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醒目的、具有警示意涵的紅色，甚至不需要特意抬頭就能看到。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它逐漸籠罩了原本灰濛濛的昏暗天幕，也覆蓋了地面的一切。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……軍隊。;烏薩斯軍隊的警示燈。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line115", "option2": "line115"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "他們已經來了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line117"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4208_wintim_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼……", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#4$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼軍隊會在這個時候深入遠北？他們根本不應該來到這裡！", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#4$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，西北方五公里處偵測到大規模的高能源石反應，有人在快速向我們靠近。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#6$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……馬上回到研究所。;必須立刻告知阿米婭。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line126", "option2": "line126"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": 