", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯……通訊設備在這裡。我沒用過這種東西，不確定它能傳遞訊號的距離有多遠。", "name": "科謝尼婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4208_wintim_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是烏薩斯軍用通訊器。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你認識這種裝置？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line174"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Raidian有類似的裝置——她年輕的時候曾參與過烏薩斯軍方類似設備的研究，沒想到他們竟然已經做出成果了。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果和我知道的一樣，那這就是一種高性能全域訊息廣播裝置。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它具有一個功率極高的施術單元——功率大概相當於同時使用一百台普通軍用級通訊器。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的設計初衷，就是為了能向大範圍內的軍用設施發送緊急電報。當然，擅長使用感知類源石技藝的人，比如Raidian，也能接收到。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "figure_art": "avg_4179_monstr_1#2$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這難道不是好事？;你為什麼這麼緊張？", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line183", "option2": "line183"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4179_monstr_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是它沒有辦法發送出特定頻段的訊號。", "name": "Mon3tr"}, "fi